  "titles": "Zardu Layak The Crimson Apostle, The Thrice-Born, The Binder of Souls, The Voice of the Unspeaking",
  "lore": "Zardu Layak’s true name is lost to time but he took the name he now bears some time after his Legion’s punishment at Monorchia. He came to be known as the Crimson Apostle for his fiery raiment and the scalding blood in which he daubed his armour. Suffused in dark powers that he uses to destroy minds and bodies, Zardu Layak walks his bloody path accompanied by hulking bodyguards, the Anakatis Kul each corrupted by the warped xenos blades bestowed upon them by their dark master.",
